  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its design, would constitute an incongruous and unsympathetic form of development that is unacceptable in design terms, to the detriment of the character and appearance of the host building and wider Mare Street Conservation Area. As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D3 (Optimising Site Capacity Through the Design-Led Approach), D6 (Housing Quality and Standards) and HC1 (Heritage Conservation and Growth) of the London Plan 2021, policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character), LP3 (Designated Heritage Assets) and LP17 (Housing Design) of the Hackney Local Plan 2033 and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;/p&gt;"
